{
  "stem": "10181.5",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But those who could were taken to nearby-- like a dispersement camp, where, you know, where they checked out who you were, where you wanted to go to.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And you couldn't go everywhere yet because this was in May-- May '45.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And-- the major-- like Amsterdam-- these places had only been liberated, really, May 8, you know, when the war was over.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So-- and-- and they also had suffered-- also had suffered from starvation.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So you-- they couldn't send people there in any case.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They had to wait.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But we were taken off the train, my sister and myself, because we were very sick.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I think I had-- had developed typhus by that time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I was taken to one hospital, and my sister was taken to a different hospital.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I was taken to a hospital which-- Maastricht was very Catholic.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And at the time, all the nurses were nuns.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And not only that, I was taken to a hospital which was inside a convent.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It was a temporary hospital which had been established.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And strangely enough, I was the only Jew-- the only kid there and the only Jew-- because the rest were all people who had-- men who had come back from under-- you know, who had served in the-- fought in the underground and been-- been caught and been brought back to Holland.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And very soon, most of the people also were Catholics.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Every morning there was sort of a-- a priest came to make mass, and they noticed that I didn't participate so they knew I was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "You know, they didn't-- didn't bother me and I-- let me sleep.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And they took all my clothes and burned it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "You know, this was-- this was the thing to do.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Of course I was left without anything, but that was OK, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I had just-- had pajamas or whatever.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And basically, they tried to treat me, you know, and make sure that I didn't overeat, you know, because the food at that time was there.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "There was plenty of food.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And they were very careful with the diet they gave me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And they tried to make it nice for me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And-- and-- what they did-- it was one big room where we lived, you know, in the hospital.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "There was, I don't know, maybe 20, 30 men in that room.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And there was a balcony next to the room.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And they put my bed on the balcony in order to be out in the fresh air.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And they had a-- they ran sort of a-- a school-- no, not a nursery school-- a school they ran at the same time, the nuns, for Dutch kids in the area.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "So they used to come by in the morning and sing songs for me when I was lying in bed and-- in order to be sort of friendly and nice to sort of cheer me up.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And after about two or three weeks or maybe-- yeah, something like that-- I was able to get up.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "I wasn't able to walk, [? actually, ?] and-- when I-- but I was able to get up.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And I walked.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "Not very well, but I walked.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And I wanted to go and see my sister.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And she was in the regular hospital, also run by nuns, but in the regular hospital.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And I went to see my sister.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And the worst-- first thing she said to me, your teeth have grown.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Because, you know, nothing grows in-- in-- in those conditions, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And I had-- the teeth-- my teeth had grown bigger, whatever, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "That's the first thing she noticed.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
